{"tid":178244,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"(逃兵）搵夠錢先移民定直接去闖？","createTime":"2017-03-29T11:48:15.000Z","updateTime":"2017-03-29T15:19:09.000Z","uid":28031,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"f0962494a327a417b7b54216fbcf1629ab5ff354","tid":178244,"uid":28031,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-29T11:48:15.000Z","msg":"巴絲打會點簡？"},{"pid":"28fd47c5d0573b2b7026e9af62ee6696009840e4","tid":178244,"uid":1582,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-29T12:12:47.000Z","msg":"闖<br />\n你喺香港唔會搵夠錢"},{"pid":"7c6ef1d7a22451dc611147fff68ab8d8249c5f61","tid":178244,"uid":95584,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-29T12:54:18.000Z","msg":"緊係闖啦巴打<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n趁後生去闖 你可能闖出一片新天地<br />\n出去闖你起碼知道果邊咩環境<br />\n可能果邊係未如你理想嘅 到時你都可以走<br />\n如果你真係中意果邊 都可以靠打工居留 <br />\n慢慢再諗點樣移民<br />\n<br />\n重點係人會變 你而家想移民<br />\n但到你搵夠錢老左可能已經唔再係咁諗<br />\n又或者你係香港做死一世都搵唔夠錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n趁你仲有心有力有時間出去闖蕩<br />\n就算失敗都起碼叫做試過<br />\n唔好比自己有遺憾呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0e70d207f4a59f64543b401c1d68b23f0f8d92ab","tid":178244,"uid":20241,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-29T12:55:34.000Z","msg":"搵多少少先<br />\n一年生活費<br />\n當買個保險<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f242c7fae26da8043eee6fb84c9adc975b8e79fd","tid":178244,"uid":78429,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-29T13:05:40.000Z","msg":"闖啦<br />\n<br />\n香港你有能力儲就唔會想移民"},{"pid":"4aa4de2e3931a7ff39936f89c81cc3d9be5644e1","tid":178244,"uid":30561,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-29T13:14:04.000Z","msg":"闖啦<br />\n<br />\n好快香港上流嘅職位大部份都會比大陸人取代。"},{"pid":"7f7ec7ad29691190fb1e4ef261e051a625ea523c","tid":178244,"uid":23180,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-29T13:18:25.000Z","msg":"直接去闖"},{"pid":"592554811c67ad3ac130722b46351f234a45f85c","tid":178244,"uid":93986,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-29T13:21:18.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>闖啦<br />\n<br />\n好快香港上流嘅職位大部份都會比大陸人取代。</blockquote><br />\n正確，香港競爭只會愈來愈大。<br />\n要搵大錢，一定要去返窮些的國家拼搏<br />\n但一定好危險<br />\n如果想平穩就等拎公屋算"},{"pid":"8376e6f7697557b8ecce6d654f6800939625fb94","tid":178244,"uid":28031,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-29T14:11:00.000Z","msg":"全部人都講去闖<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n如果去生活水平低嘅國家呢？"},{"pid":"a699e563e624c4668aaa0ac56366b31677d0ce3b","tid":178244,"uid":78429,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-29T14:34:37.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>全部人都講去闖<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n如果去生活水平低嘅國家呢？</blockquote><br />\n一樣"},{"pid":"7dec4f436dd4373c71ff8018a271b388e6394807","tid":178244,"uid":1582,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-29T15:05:49.000Z","msg":"人地國家唔同職業都有向上流動性<br />\n香港？你打份牛工咋"},{"pid":"c50483ba880ff4f564a38f103b6dfcf46c332c1e","tid":178244,"uid":51753,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-29T15:19:09.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>人地國家唔同職業都有向上流動性<br />\n香港？你打份牛工咋</blockquote><br />\n美國加拿大都算<br />\n係歐洲 唔係白人都係有個玻璃天花 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}